        <h1>Who we are...</h1>
        <div class="body">
          <br/>
          <p>VeteranReady is a consulting company based in Las Vegas. Our mission is to support Nevada businesses and non-profit agencies by providing consulting, training, and event planning services that focus on building up the community. Our clients understand that veterans play an integral role in strengthening the community and that it's not just the right thing to do, it's the smart thing to do.</p>
